{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"纪念堂工地的路","authors":["陈松叶"],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":3,"day":20}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念堂工地的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京市房修二公司工人　陈松叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去纪念堂工地的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"环绕在天安门前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八盏红灯照亮征途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗迎风招展……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望雄伟的天安门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八角楼、遵义城高耸眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俯视欢腾的金水河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南湖水、延河浪流过心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，纪念碑前请停一停："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让毛主席的亲密战友走在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队前——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛是，周恩来总理从远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方带回捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛是，杨开慧烈士从湘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江寄来思念……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建立毛主席纪念堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席代表了人民的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸烂万恶“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席舒展了时代的容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席亲自为基石培"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席亲自把大路挑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席挥锹起风雷呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路才这样坚实、这样宽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路呵，永远奔腾时代的洪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通向共产主义明天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走呵，向着红太阳高声歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席纪念堂工地宏伟、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}